        <headline>Warning to Sheep Graziers for North East Pastoral and Flinders forecast districts</headline>
        <description>Sheep graziers are warned that cold temperatures and southerly winds are expected during Friday. Areas likely to be affected include parts of the Flinders and North East Pastoral forecast districts. There is a risk of losses of lambs and sheep exposed to these conditions.</description>
